Name: Tech Invaders TD
About the game: In Tech Invaders are your task, to kill the hackers with Annoing Child, an Expert Team, A SoMe Army and many others! Basic Game In the basis Tower Defence part of the game, are your mision to kill all the hackers in the 20+ maps. When you complete 1 map, you will get Coins, XP and maby Gems! For the Coins can you buy Bonus Levels And gems can you use for Game Upgrades ! Basic Game - Features - Buy Bonuslevels - Upgrade your count of defenders - Play over 20 maps - No ads Expert Team When you reach level 20, can you upgrade a Tech Expert, as you can use ingame. If it is fully upgraded, can it insta-kill some hackers Expert Team - Features - Upgrade Range - Upgrade Damage - Upgrade Speed So what are you waiting for? Buy and Play Tech Invaders NOW! (From 7/10)
